    "• RST Odd: We assign values of 1 at odd positions and 0 at even positions in the RST matrix.",
    "• RST Random: We assign random values ∈ [0, 1] ⊆ R to the RST matrix without considering the probability of discourse relations.",
    "In ablation experiments, we use Vicuna as backbone for testing.",
    "The motivation behind setting these three ablation conditions is to simulate the extreme scenario where the RST parser completely fails to deliver valuable discourse information.",
